vn.map4d.map.core

Class MFProjection

  • java.lang.Object
    • vn.map4d.map.core.MFProjection

  • public final class MFProjection
extends java.lang.Object
    A projection is used to translate between on screen location and geographic coordinates on the surface of the Earth (MFLocationCoordinate). Screen location is in screen pixels (not display pixels) with respect to the top left corner of the map (and not necessarily of the whole screen).
